<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, uns
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etliche <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kauffleute fürbraht, wie daz in etwievil
                        habe und kauffmanschaft in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> gnedigen
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, herczog Fridrichs von Österreich
                                <expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>herschäfft<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und gepieten bekümert sein worden. <expan>Bite<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisze,
                        daz ir durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> dinste
                            <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günstige <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gen
                                <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, herczog <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>,
                        beweysen wöllet, daz in dieselb ir habe und kauffmanschaft on hindernüsse
                        volge und ledig werde, als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in vigilia
                                <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan>
<expan>Barth<ex>olomei</ex></expan>
<expan>ap<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
